    <item>
      <title>意大利联合信贷银行拨出 2.28 亿欧元与俄罗斯资产扣押有关</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/unicredit-sets-aside-228-million-linked-to-russia-asset-seizure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利联合信贷银行首席执行官安德里亚·奥塞尔 (Andrea Orcel) 在接受采访时表示，该银行“审慎拨出” 2.28 亿欧元（2.47 亿美元）与俄罗斯法院扣押该国资产的决定有关的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/unicredit-sets-aside-228-million-linked-to-russia-asset-seizure</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 08:34:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韦丹塔寻求合作伙伴开发正在恢复的赞比亚矿山</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/vedanta-seeks-partners-to-develop-zambia-mines-it-s-regaining</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁阿尼尔·阿加瓦尔 (Anil Agarwal) 创立的矿业公司韦丹塔资源有限公司 (Vedanta Resources Ltd.) 正在寻找商业合作伙伴，以提高赞比亚铜矿的产量。经过多年的法律纠纷后，该公司重新获得了对赞比亚铜矿的控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/vedanta-seeks-partners-to-develop-zambia-mines-it-s-regaining</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 08:31:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非通胀率因食品价格放缓至六个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/south-african-inflation-slows-as-food-and-transport-costs-cool</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非 6 月份通胀率小幅下降，触及六个月低点，这可能促使央行考虑在今年晚些时候削减借贷成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/south-african-inflation-slows-as-food-and-transport-costs-cool</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 08:12:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
